episodes.title: The Intro to IBLP and the Beginning of Indoctrination [Part 1: IBLP Cult]
episodes.description:
Before I was born, my parents were introduced to the IBLP cult and a Landmark Baptist church. I explain how this happened and give my thoughts on a few things that resulted. I share how my mom was planning my abortion and why. I also process in real-time a detail of a story my mom has told countless times. 



#cultsurvivor #iblp
